# Funnel Components

- Funnel-only UI lives in `src/components/funnels`.
- Use `Funnel` prefix for primitive components (`FunnelHero`, `FunnelCTABox`, etc.).
- Rendering order must come from `componentOrder` through `componentMap`, not from hardcoded JSX order.
- Keep components reusable and content-driven via typed props.
- Do not import funnel-specific config JSON directly in UI primitives.
